<title>slmtk ạlḥyạẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr slmtk ạlḥyạh yạ mnbʿ ạlḥyạh
 (sd ʿlyhạ bạlrḍạ yạ gẖạyẗ ạlmnạ)2
 1- nfsy ạ̹lyk trnw dwmạaⁿ ạ̹lyk ạ̉sẖdw
 (fy kl ywm jdyd ḥby ạ̹lyk yzyd)2
 bnwrk ạlnwr ạ̉ry̱ yạ gẖạyẗ ạlmnạ
 2- kẖwfy̱ ạlmryr tsẖdwạ wạlʿmr mʿk yḥlw
 ( ạ̉nt ạlmlạdẖ ạlwḥyd wạlstr fyk ạ̉kyd)2
 fạ̉mktẖ mʿy llmnthy yạ gẖạyẗ ạlmnạ
 3- dʿny ạ̹lyk ạ̉dnw sẖwqy ạ̹lyk ynmw
 (ạ̉nt ạlmḥb ạlfryd ymnạk kẖyr tzyd)2
 ạ̉ny lk ṭwl ạlmdy̱ yạ gẖạyẗ ạlmnạ</lyrics>
